node.text:
⁣Join the premiere here 🚨🎥
https://urlgeni.us/youtube/3_zu⠀ 
HOW TO BE HAPPY? Start With Why (Documentary 2020)⠀ ⠀ ⠀ 
Based on The True Story of @cameron.fous.
⠀ ⠀ ⠀ 
Beginning with naive expectations we grow up with: that wealth and success leads to happiness the solution to all your problems.
⠀ ⠀ ⠀ ⠀ 
How Social media has pushed the envelope of what happiness and success is supposed to look like... To the point where influencers are now stuck portraying a fantasy instead of their real-life with the pressure to constantly outdo themselves and the ‘competition’. All while driving insecurity and life-damaging⠀ comparisons to their audience. An endless⠀ loop of chaos fuelling a worldwide mental health epidemic.
⠀ ⠀ ⠀ 
@cameron.fous lived the fantasy. He threw the parties, made millions until... … it all ended in disaster, in a constant state of depression, and not knowing why or how to⠀ fix it.⠀ ⠀ ⠀

And now? He's calling out his own BS.. his own mistakes.. and revealing the 4 Secrets to⠀ happiness he discovered over his 15 years as an entrepreneur, and helping others find their⠀ true calling in the game of entrepreneurship: to pursue a life of fulfillment instead of chasing money that leads to an empty road.
⠀ ⠀ ⠀ ⁣
This Film is his life Story. This is his road to Iconic.⠀ ⠀ ⠀ 
Ask yourself… Are you happy? If you are seeking a deeper fulfilment in life, deeper purpose,⠀ a deeper understanding of what happiness means and how to achieve it from someone whohas been through it all... This documentary is for you.⠀ ⠀ ⠀ 
Join the “Are You Happy?” Premiere Dec 15th at 8pm Est here🚨🎥 https://urlgeni.us/youtube/3_zu⠀
